definition: any/either
surname Ren/Ren County 任縣|任县[Ren2 Xian4] in Hebei

to assign/to appoint/to take up a post/office/responsibility/to let/to allow/to give free rein to/no matter (how, what etc)/classifier for terms served in office, or for spouses, girlfriends etc (as in 前任男友)
one/1/single/a (article)/as soon as/entire/whole/all/throughout/"one" radical in Chinese characters (Kangxi radical 1)/also pr. [yao1] for greater clarity when spelling out numbers digit by digit
any one of (a list of possibilities)

sentences.english: He said she never supported any particular presidential candidate.
sentences.chinese: 他說她從未支持過任一總統候選人。

sentences.english: Otherwise, that means none of these three points are connected and hence they are mutual strangers.
sentences.chinese: 否則，表示任一三個點都不相連，他們互相不認識。

sentences.english: You can pass any one variable to a function at most once in the argument list.
sentences.chinese: 你最多隻能把任一變量傳入參數表中一次。

sentences.english: You Got Spark, Kid-5 Reach level 5in any single class in Multiplayer.
sentences.chinese: 在多人模式中，任一職業的等級到達5。

sentences.english: The latter is the largest order placed by any Scandinavian airline.
sentences.chinese: 後者是任一斯堪的納維亞定期航線的最大定單。

sentences.english: To sort the components listed, select any column heading.
sentences.chinese: 若要排序上列元件，請選取任一資料行行首。

sentences.english: The motion of any node in the model only couples with those in its neighborhood.
sentences.chinese: 這一模型中任一節點的運動僅與其鄰近的節點耦聯。

sentences.english: The system first learns a churn prediction model by the decision tree-based technique from a historical subscriber database.
sentences.chinese: 本模組可用來預測任一輸入用戶之流失率。

sentences.english: Business Industrial Network disclaims any and all rights in those marks.
sentences.chinese: 企業工業網絡放棄中的任一和在那些標記所有權益。

sentences.english: It will also mount to any vehicle.
sentences.chinese: 這樣將等同於任一交通工具。

sentences.english: Click or drag corners of the page to go forward or backward.
sentences.chinese: 單擊或拖拉頁面任一角落即可換頁。

sentences.english: If you have any of those signs, do not go to work or school.
sentences.chinese: 如果你有任一一項跡象，不要去工作或上學。

sentences.english: A backup is performed if any of the criteria specified are true.
sentences.chinese: 如果所指定的任一條件爲真，則執行備份操作。

sentences.english: The second is that he didn't discarded 90 % of the brain from any mouse.
sentences.chinese: 拉什利始終沒有拋棄任一老鼠大腦的90%。

sentences.english: These forces may begin as tiny pods within the space between of any given field.
sentences.chinese: 這些勢力可能以任一能量場間隔空間中的小密團開始。

sentences.english: You can go either way , you know.
sentences.chinese: 你能去任一方法，你知道。
